{
  "3045660": {
    "name": "东方醉游稽传~Touhou Drunken Rebellion",
    "steam_appid": 3045660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>背景故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幻想乡的小妖怪们早已看清：不管是在异变解决过程中还是在日常生活之中，以博丽巫女为首的家伙们从不顾虑她们的感受，肆意的欺压她们。忍无可忍之际，小妖怪们决定反击——成立“妖怪悔改组织”，并以一间热闹非凡的妖怪酒吧为据点，四处招揽有志之士，誓要在这场华丽的下克上中，讨回属于自己的公道！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/dacef9050ff22161ad3caa741a7e4c61.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/dacef9050ff22161ad3caa741a7e4c61.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/dacef9050ff22161ad3caa741a7e4c61.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方醉游稽传 ~ Touhou Drunken Rebellion》是一款俯视角弹幕射击Roguelike游戏，玩家在游戏中将扮演幻想乡中的小妖怪，向幻想乡的强权发起一场酣畅淋漓的下克上之战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从据点出发，打倒遇到的每一个敌人吧！使用华丽且伤害爆炸的弹幕火拼或运用特殊能力和技巧进行作战，并沿路收集效果各异的“酒品”，打倒最后的boss，圆满完成作战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/0cb1ff9fec05adc7cd392c3893dd1d57.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/0cb1ff9fec05adc7cd392c3893dd1d57.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/0cb1ff9fec05adc7cd392c3893dd1d57.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可选角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~被遗忘的唐伞妖怪~ 多多良小伞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/b56fd5b1f0d0a7fc3b6b0ded58e20d3d.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/b56fd5b1f0d0a7fc3b6b0ded58e20d3d.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/b56fd5b1f0d0a7fc3b6b0ded58e20d3d.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天然呆的小妖怪，为了要回灵梦拖欠的工钱加入了悔改组织，拥有所有角色中最高的初始数值和生存能力最高的技能，近战流派的强度也很高，朴实无华的强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~嫉妒缠身的桥姬妖怪~ 水桥帕露西</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/70665d0ef28d445601b3535a0169a316.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/70665d0ef28d445601b3535a0169a316.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/70665d0ef28d445601b3535a0169a316.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从地底过来的妖怪，每时每刻都在嫉妒。虽然性格别扭，但某种意义上也很可爱，据她本人所说加入悔改组织是为了追求更好的生活。普通情况下的战力平平无奇，可一旦被击中就会让她的嫉妒心大爆发，尽情使用她跟敌人相爱相杀吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~弱小的无名读书妖怪~ 朱鹭子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/3b87da7029c9fae1ca8ecad8de790b1a.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/3b87da7029c9fae1ca8ecad8de790b1a.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/3b87da7029c9fae1ca8ecad8de790b1a.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜爱看书的文学妖怪，身体素质很弱。由于过去经常被灵梦和魔理沙欺负，所以对巫女意见很大。性格上比较自卑，战斗上也是最为特殊的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有两颗心，初始状态下全部能力都非常低，使用书籍做为武器，无法升级技能，看起来相当的弱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>但是给她一些成长的时间，也许就会出人意料...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/ac3083a4ecb030465224340acdd4d9be.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/ac3083a4ecb030465224340acdd4d9be.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/ac3083a4ecb030465224340acdd4d9be.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~紧闭的恋之瞳~ 古明地恋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/fe4352e3211d0818a4c3906b4207fef1.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/fe4352e3211d0818a4c3906b4207fef1.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/fe4352e3211d0818a4c3906b4207fef1.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在作战的过程中有可能会出现的神秘又可爱的妖怪，在战胜她三次之后，居然可以让她成为我们的同伴？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会利用无意识的力量在敌群之间来回穿梭，并利用独特的技能打出大量的爆发伤害，她的加入又会让作战产生怎样的变数呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来还会有更多妖怪加入……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>华丽desu！眼花缭乱的各式弹幕</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一种弹幕都有其独特的作用。作为装备安装在武器上，以最华丽的方式倾泻火力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/8daf6327af4fec62aeda8b64a1ee99d4.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/8daf6327af4fec62aeda8b64a1ee99d4.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/8daf6327af4fec62aeda8b64a1ee99d4.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来还会有更多的弹幕！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>酒，还有更多酒</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >古来强者皆寂寞，惟有饮者留其名！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有着各式各样的酒，会为玩家提供多种被动效果。在不同的情况下，搭配合适的酒类、角色被动和弹幕也是成为强者的条件。让“假酒”和“弹幕”相互组合，直达爽快醉意的巅峰时刻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/a83a23e024c8eaacb7f115ca3d5b58df.avif?t=1763699679\" width=730 height=718 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来还会有更多的酒！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收藏室</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >酒吧的下方有一个收藏室，妖怪们会将收集到的弹幕和酒放在储藏室中，让大家品味品味</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/2d404468995a29adba96469714707a32.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/2d404468995a29adba96469714707a32.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/2d404468995a29adba96469714707a32.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过可不能把东西偷偷带出储藏室哦，这是规定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强敌</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>雾雨魔理沙</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决异变的魔法使，妖怪们的下克上目标之一，擅长高火力魔法，最近在研发蘑菇弹幕，会释放大量的星星弹幕攻击我方</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/9ac5129039e957256aea5c9d15b123d4.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/9ac5129039e957256aea5c9d15b123d4.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/9ac5129039e957256aea5c9d15b123d4.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>博丽灵梦</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决异变的巫女，被众多小妖怪们恐惧着，是下克上作战的主要目标，虽然是个懒散的不讲理巫女，但是战斗力十分强大，妖怪们真的能战胜她么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/f2fa73f688d57a9c40ff54633d2ef1eb.poster.avif?t=1763699679\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/f2fa73f688d57a9c40ff54633d2ef1eb.webm?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045660/extras/f2fa73f688d57a9c40ff54633d2ef1eb.mp4?t=1763699679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来还会有更多的强敌！</p>",
